description.content:
Hello,

Get your e-commerce stores, listing, membership, and booking websites done today.

 

Feel free to contact me if you already have a website and want it converted to an e-commerce store or if you want things started from scratch :)

 

====== E-commerce services =======

  • WordPress installation
  • Theme and Plugin Installation and Customization
  • Mobile and tablet-friendly layout
  • Modern UI/UX
  • Shipping and Tax Module (on Demand)
  • Payment integration
  • Professional slider
  • Shopping cart and checkout
  • Wishlist
  • My account panel
  • Live chat
  • Complete on-page SEO (on demand)
  • Coupon system
  • Contact Us page with a map
  • Subscriber form (which converts your visitors into customers)
  • Automatic invoice for every buyer, etc.

 

Why choose me?   

  • 100% Customer Satisfaction
  • Proven experience in making multi-nature websites.
  • Unlimited revision until satisfied
  • Ongoing support (on-demand with gig extras)
  • Quick delivery of your project
  • Result-oriented website creation

 

Please inbox me with your project specifications so we can do requirements elicitation first :)

questionsAndAnswers.question: What information do you need from me to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: In order to start the project, I will require access to your hosting details and WordPress dashboard. Moreover, it would be useful if you could provide any branding materials or specific content that you wish to be included on the site.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you design a custom e-commerce website tailored to my brand?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! I am capable of designing an Ecommerce website that is both distinctive and aesthetically pleasing, while also reflecting your brand's identity and goals.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you assist with integrating payment gateways on my site?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! I can seamlessly integrate popular payment gateways, allowing your customers to make secure online transactions.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I need additional features or functionality on my e-commerce site?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Please feel free to share any ideas you have for customizing or adding features. I am open to discussing your needs and will do my best to accommodate them.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide SEO-friendly e-commerce solutions?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I make sure to prioritize SEO best practices when creating your website, so that it is well-optimized for search engines and has improved visibility.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How long does it take to complete an Ecommerce project?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The timeline can vary depending on the complexity of the project. Upon discussing your specific requirements, I can provide an estimated delivery time.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer post-project support and maintenance?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I offer post-project support and maintenance packages to ensure your Ecommerce website runs smoothly and stays up-to-date.

notableClients.name: Skwer Group
notableClients.interaction_description: Skwer Group offers setting offshore company accounts. I've helped them automate the process so there is a smooth client onboarding process, payment gateway integration, generating invoices as a PDF, and automatic e-mails on application submission.

enriched_details.name: Skwer Group
enriched_details.description: Skwer Group offers online offshore business setup services.

notableClients.name: LMGI - Location Manager Guild International
notableClients.interaction_description: I've automated the application collection process for LMGI annual awards. The project involved Formidable Form customization, google docs and google drive integration. We generated files on submission and saved them in appropriate folders.

enriched_details.name: Location Managers Guild International
enriched_details.description: The Locations Managers Guild International is a professional organization of location managers, location scouts, assistant location managers, and affiliated business members, such as film commissions, location services, vendors, and filming venues.

notableClients.name: SpiraleEd Solutions
notableClients.interaction_description: I've set up a system where quiz is taken by students and the results are generated and saved into a result summary file for each class subject, teachers are then given access to these files automatically. The work involved Jotform, make.com, Gdrive.

enriched_details.name: SpiralEdSolutions
enriched_details.description: Our commitment is to provide teachers with quality, spiraled materials to develop classrooms where success is possible for all students. SpiralEd Solutions is a Texas based education company formed and operated by current Texas educators.

notableClients.name: WEMULCH
notableClients.interaction_description: wemulch.com connects end users on-demand with landclearing or forestry professionals. I've customized their website directory side using Formidable forms, and Woocommerce. Javascript. PHP, HTML, CSS were used in the development process.
